A new survey from Echelon Insights, which is partnering with Puck for exclu=
sive polling on the 2024 electorate, suggests that the tolerant-but-tough m=
essage is working. In one of the
few surveys conducted entirely after the D.N.C., a poll of likely voters co=
nducted from Friday to Sunday found Harris running about even with Trump on=
